SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT PRD010.PLN_CD , PRD010.DDMMYYYY , PRD010.DAY_WEK , PRD010.WEEK_NO FROM PRD010 WHERE PRD010.PLN_CD NOT LIKE '_' AND PRD010.PLN_CD NOT LIKE '__AE' AND PRD010.PLN_CD NOT LIKE '__AF' AND SUBSTR ( PRD010.DDMMYYYY , 1 , 6) = ':1' AND PRD010.OPE_TYP <> '0' AND EXISTS ( SELECT * FROM PRD004 WHERE PRD010.PLN_CD = PRD004.PLN_CD) ORDER BY PRD010.PLN_CD , PRD010.DDMMYYYY
